e":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"75d689f88d0a07e530154c850dd2503ce854361b","tid":2266300,"uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"6755893ccfb879addfefadf461638fb59d6725d0","tid":2266300,"uid":326017,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T08:14:02.000Z","msg":"都唔係問題<br />\n但連做教練都未有成績就扮哂野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T09:52:18.000Z","msg":"扮德高望重既名宿 球員時期只係個二三線球員"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T09:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本唔知佢係乜水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:24:02.000Z","msg":"愛華頓名宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc67bb6fd03bfe2f7efd5c7ab255e79ac431194","tid":2266300,"uid":73089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"523c77a7b4b66a6800723f2bee3daeecc4b1ccba","tid":2266300,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T07:59:55.000Z","msg":"奧斯爾遭阿仙奴除名引起的風波，領隊阿迪達竟堅稱自己已盡最大努力給予這位中場機會，還表示現時的情況已是<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">對球會最好的方案</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n自3月7日對韋斯咸最後一次替阿仙奴上陣，奧斯爾在英超復賽後及新球季展開都一直坐冷板，至早前更被兵工廠踢出英超大軍名單外，令不少人猜測是否因早前替維吾爾族發聲得罪了中共，以致這位每周拿35萬鎊堪稱全隊最高薪的球員，落得如此下場。<br />\n<br />\n不過，阿迪達周五接受天空體育訪問，就堅持自己已盡了最大努力：「我可以告訴你們的，就是我已盡了最大努力，在我的能力範圍內給了他最多機會。從我的角度，我一直很忍耐地給他機會，而且很公平。」<br />\n<br />\n他續謂：「奧斯爾是球會過去幾季的重要一員，我絕對尊重，但也必須作出決定，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">這個決定對球隊和球會都是最好的</span></span>。當我這樣做，我就要向他們給出我的原因和答案，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">我已經給了我的理由</span></span>，他們相信或同意我與否，那不是我能控制的，但我的決定是跟從內心和腦袋所想的，所以我認為是最好的。」<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201031/5273RFQMDRGLLFREFVW65TS25U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201031%2F5273RFQMDRGLLFREFVW65TS25U%2F&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=abb19645\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201031%2F5273RFQMDRGLLFREFVW65TS25U%2F&h=305b9d05\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201031/5273RFQMDRGLLFREFVW65TS25U/</a><br />\n<br />\n阿迪達真係好撚低賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:27:08.000Z","msg":"有無佢twitter 上去屌柒佢先"},{"pid":"a96cdee432c960351708fa27aea36b3fec1eea45","tid":2266300,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"a7232f5deb417af577c6467110a94af2484efb3a","tid":2266300,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1c11ee1f861d3665f4d8c82f9d0f27fc083518f8","tid":2266300,"uid":289946,"like":2,"dislike":53,"score":-51,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T08:01:37.000Z","msg":"咁奧燒的確係廢。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T09:47:03.000Z","msg":"你老母就廢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:35:37.000Z","msg":"唔好人身攻擊"},{"pid":"a52073a28d10fe44061775b4847151ead7504288","tid":2266300,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"係咪做隊友個時有私怨"},{"pid":"7fc9d59ae99ef45ed0d18bc105a181196f48b579","tid":2266300,"uid":25771,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"0714c20c91a0e8de037e15e64e9fd0775f2e4654","tid":2266300,"uid":1810,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T08:01:44.000Z","msg":"俾個垃圾中場做教練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />向個世界級攻中指指點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:37:56.000Z","msg":"得施丹可以教波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce99821571c91728d0ae21c8ffbbcb9bacc77ba","tid":2266300,"uid":173060,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:44:23.000Z","msg":"球員果陣係幾鐘意佢既<br />\n唔係勁，但實用<br />\n雲爺爺果陣就算踢得差我都有心會睇下波<br />\n依家阿迪達做領隊成班波搞到睇都唔想睇<br />\n以前有段時間都唔鐘意奧燒但事實係佢有能力<br />\n依家俾堆垃圾幾會出場都唔俾俾奧燒出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ebb